11:09.083 --> 11:11.041
General Washington?

11:09.083 --> 11:11.041
Paranoid. No.

11:09.083 --> 11:11.041
Mm.

11:11.041 --> 11:12.750
Yes. December 1776,

11:12.750 --> 11:14.916
the Colonial troops

11:12.750 --> 11:14.916
