11:25.916 --> 11:28.500
Betsy Ross.

11:28.500 --> 11:30.875
Your ancestor and my trusted

11:28.500 --> 11:30.875
companion knew one another?

11:30.875 --> 11:32.916
No name's given,

11:30.875 --> 11:32.916
