12:43.125 --> 12:45.250
If you have any sanity left,

12:43.125 --> 12:45.250
General,

12:45.250 --> 12:48.750
I entreat you to

12:45.250 --> 12:48.750
take this medicine.

12:51.583 --> 12:54.083
General Howe must have

12:51.583 --> 12:54.083
